ent-MedievalClothingOuterRoyalArmorLeatherLight = snow-white leather armor
    .desc = Tanned armor made from multiple layers of leather. Some sections have been dyed and decorated in the colors of the renowned merchant dynasty "Whitelight". The armor has been shaped and reinforced, allowing it to be worn lightly with great flexibility of movement. This armor is the most accessible among the family's infantry.
ent-MedievalClothingOuterRoyalArmorLeather = light vest
    .desc = A lightweight leather vest without overlays or shoulder elements, designed to snugly fit the chest and provide some protection. The leather quality is top-tier, with dyed elements of thin fabric and leather layers stretched over it. The overlay colors associate it with the "Whitelight" dynasty.
