ent-MedievalClothingOuterLeafRoyalArmorLeatherHeavy = leaf armor
    .desc = The entire armor is decorated and reinforced with patches. Its light and flexible form allows for an advantage over the enemy due to speed. The armor itself has a magical coating that protects against moisture and damage.
